            <li>Freeport McMoRan, 2013. Strength in Resources: 2013 Working Toward Sustainable Development Report, Phoenix, Arizona. <a class="Article-link" href="http://www.fcx.com/sd/pdf/WTSD_Bk_2013.pdf">http://www.fcx.com/sd/pdf/WTSD_Bk_2013.pdf</a></li>
            <li>Sakhalin Energy Investment Company, Ltd., 2013. Sustainable Development Report, Sakhalin Island, Russia. <a class="Article-link" href="http://www.sakhalinenergy.com/media/user/otchety/GRI_2013_Eng.pdf">http://www.sakhalinenergy.com/media/user/otchety/GRI_2013_Eng.pdf</a></li>
            <li>Davis, Rachel and Daniel Franks, 2014. “Costs of Company-Community Conflict in the Extractive Sector,” Harvard Kennedy School, Corporate Social Responsibility Initiative Report No. 66, Cambridge, MA. <a class="Article-link" href="http://www.hks.harvard.edu/m-rcbg/CSRI/research/Costs%20of%20Conflict_Davis%20%20Franks.pdf">http://www.hks.harvard.edu/m-rcbg/CSRI/research/Costs%20of%20Conflict_Davis%20%20Franks.pdf</a></li>
